### Cooldown Class

```markdown
### Cooldown Class
#### Description
A cooldown class to prevent repeated actions within a certain time frame.

#### Properties
* `cooldownTime`: The time in milliseconds before the cooldown can be reset.
* `lastUse`: The timestamp of the last time the cooldown was used.

#### Methods
* `isOnCooldown()`: Checks if the cooldown is active.
* `resetCooldown()`: Resets the cooldown timer.
```

### Cooldown Class Code
```javascript
class Cooldown {
  constructor(cooldownTime) {
    this.cooldownTime = cooldownTime;
    this.lastUse = 0;
  }

  isOnCooldown() {
    const currentTime = Date.now();
